First, this:
https://www.maketecheasier.com/play-sound-through-multiple-devices-linux/

-> enable simultaneous, dual playback settings for pulse-audio throught `paprefs`

Second:
https://askubuntu.com/a/78179/916353

-> Using `pavucontrol-qt`, go to `playback` tab and select some playback to output to `Simultaneous output to ...`

Boom, that's it!

